        {
            "title": "思格新能暗盤中段較招股價高逾70% 股份明登場",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">思格新能(06656)股份將於明天掛牌，暗盤中段較招股價324.2元高超過70%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：思格新能官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260330_FI_source-web_Sigenergy-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：思格新能官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260330_FI_source-web_Sigenergy-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：思格新能官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">輝立交易平台顯示，截至下午約5時01分，思格新能暗盤報566元，高於招股價74.58%；富途交易平台顯示的暗盤價則為589元，較招股價高81.68%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15876861-%e6%80%9d%e6%a0%bc%e6%96%b0%e8%83%bd%e6%9a%97%e7%9b%a4%e4%b8%ad%e6%ae%b5%e8%bc%83%e6%8b%9b%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e9%ab%98%e9%80%be70-%e8%82%a1%e4%bb%bd%e6%98%8e%e7%99%bb%e5%a0%b4",
